comments: Jerk,easy class kinda bc he does take home quizzes that boost your grade and leaves hw to help you study but overall doesnt teach.you learn from the book.Doesn\'t answer questions to students and doesnt even try to understand the question better if he doesnt get it. He\'s a very kind professor. His door is always open to students, and he likes to joke around. His only flaw is his English. His lecture and instructions can be confusing. I mostly learned from the book. If you are a smart student, go with him. Otherwise, you may get frustrated.
He\'s very sweet, but too confusing... Very laid back! Easy A!
